sources.title: Silver Needle in the Sky (1954) ROCKY JONES, SPACE RANGER
sources.description:
Stars: Richard Crane, Scotty Beckett, Sally Mansfield
Director: Hollingsworth Morse

You've heard of The Lone Ranger, now meet The Space Ranger! Follow the adventures of Rocky Jones and crew as they cruise the galaxy in their Orbit Jet X-V2 and defend Earth against space-bound evil doers!

metadata.Plot: Intergalactic trouble erupts for Rocky Jones and his Space Rangers as they find themselves on board a spaceship full of diplomats that's heading towards an interplanetary conference.
metadata.Actors: Richard Crane, Sally Mansfield, Maurice Cass
